dc_title_s: Rutgers University, Cook College, New Jersey 1978
dc_description_s: Map of the Rutgers University Cook College formerly the College of Agriculture and Environmental Science. Includes building directory. Map includes portion of campus in New Brunswick borough and the outlying departments in North Brunswick Township including the Rutgers Gardens property and the horticulture farms. Recently constructed buildings are named and shown in bold and instructions are printed for Route 1 traffic to approach Cook College from the College Farm Road but not from Ryders Lane.
